dmca.title: Times-Tribune Wants Image Removed [Blogger]
dmca.body:
To whom it may concern, 

It has come to my attention that a photo copyrighted to The Times-Tribune is being used without permission on a site you host - http://askcordaro.blogspot.com 

I searched the site http://askcordaro.blogspot.com for contact information but there was none. Could you please forward this request to the responsible parties and request that this copyrighted material be removed immediately. 

Supplied is the URL to the photograph in question. 

http;//bp1.blogger.com/_JMQEq_oq-s/RkBxhBv7gTI/AAAAAAAAAB8/xljDrPEGc-I/s1600-h/courthouse+project.jpg

Thank you for your timely response, 
[Private]
Interet Editor 
thetimes-thbune.com 
[Private]
[Private]@timesshamrock.com
